## What was built

**F22 вЂ” Trends page at `/trends`**

### Files created
- `src/components/trends/useTrends.ts` вЂ” Custom hook managing all trend query state. Fetches `/api/schema` on mount; fetches `/api/trends` when an event name is selected; exposes `controls`, `setters`, `series`, `numericProperties`, `loading`, `error`.
- `src/components/trends/TrendsControls.tsx` вЂ” Controls panel: event name autocomplete, native measure select (Count / Unique Users / Sum of / Avg of / Min of / Max of), conditional property autocomplete for aggregation measures, Day/Week granularity toggle, preset date chips (Last 7d/30d/90d) + custom date inputs, breakdown selector.
- `src/components/TrendChart.tsx` вЂ” Chart component with Line/Bar/Area/Table switcher, auto-switches to Bar for single-bucket data, loading skeleton, empty state, Recharts for chart rendering.
- `src/app/trends/page.tsx` вЂ” Updated to compose the full page from the three components above.
- 3 test files covering 60+ unit tests.

