**Step 2 вЂ” Hook implemented** (`src/components/users/useUserSearch.ts`):
`useUserSearch` вЂ” maintains `users`, `loading`, `hasMore`, `query`, `cursor` state. `setQuery` debounces at 300ms. `loadMore` guards against `loading || !hasMore`. Initial page fetched on mount.

**Step 3 вЂ” Page implemented** (`src/app/users/page.tsx`):
Full client component with MUI TextField (search, `data-testid="users-search"`), MUI Table (`data-testid="users-table"`) with `IdentityChip`, loading skeletons, empty state, IntersectionObserver infinite scroll, and explicit Load More fallback button.

